Package: fontquiver
Title: Set of Fonts
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Lionel", "Henry", , "lionel.hry@gmail.com", c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Provides a set of fonts with permissive licences. This
    is useful when you would like to avoid system fonts to make sure
    your outputs are reproducible.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    fontBitstreamVera (>= 0.1)
Suggests:
    testthat,
    htmltools
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
